m2, ...}] returns {s1[m1], s2[m2], ...}, which usually results in {s 1, \
Subscript[m, 1], s 2, Subscript[m, 2], ...}. FlavorThread[{s1, s2, ...}, \
{list1, list2, ...}] maps over the lists {list1, list2, ...}. \
